html is used for content and strucutres like <h1></h1>,<button></button>,<p></p> etc
css is used for decuration like shape, color, style etc
javascript is used for functionality of the contents to the websites


HTML = hyper text markup language
hyper text = like a hyper link which redirect to other page
markup langunage = write language like bold words, italic ,header tags etc in one line

<h1> opening tag
</h1> closing tag

<h1></h1> both called element

to see all elements = https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML/Element 

downloD live preview extention in vs code(right click and open show preview)

www.lipsum.com  = for lorem ipsum paragraph

<tag attribute="value" attribute="value">content</tag>

